content: Yeah, I meant to say I did a marathon, not a bike ride. I did the city's annual marathon three weeks ago, on April 10th, and I'm still feeling pretty good about it. Anyway, thanks for the pacing tips, I'll definitely keep those in mind for the bike ride. Now, can you help me with some tips on how to improve my swimming technique? I've been taking swim lessons, but I still feel like I'm not as efficient as I could be.
